This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis of tweets. The use of deep learning models such as recurrent neural networks (RNNs) and self-attention mechanisms also suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of word embeddings and backpropagation indicates that it could belong to the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
